data.name: header_home
data.comment: A button on the header that takes you to the landing page.

data.name: header_users
data.comment: A button on the header that takes you to the user listing.

data.name: header_photos
data.comment: A button on the header that takes you to a list of user-uploaded photos.

data.name: header_slots
data.comment: A button on the header that takes you to a list of user-uploaded levels. Levels are internally referred to as "slots".

data.name: header_authentication
data.comment: A button on the header that takes you to a list of authentication attempts.

data.name: header_loginRegister
data.comment: A button on the header that lets you log in or register.

data.name: header_profile
data.comment: A quick shortcut on the header to take you to your profile if logged in.

data.name: header_adminPanel
data.comment: A header link that takes you to the admin panel if available.

data.name: header_logout
data.comment: A shortcut to log you out of your account.
